  "time_ut": 1659190766,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u2019\u0bb5\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0ba9\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bc1  \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'Come and build me a house'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe has called on all members of parliament to unite to form an all-party government.",
        "The President, who visited Kandy Talatha House, also met Malwattu and Askriya Mahanayake Theras today (30).",
        "After that, the President informed the above matter at the Presidential Palace in Kandy and further said,",
        "He called upon all the parties to unite in an all-party government as the best way to recover from the country's economic crisis.",
        "He further pointed out that there is no point in raising slogans like Ranil Go Home as his house has been burnt down and please do not do so.",
        "Because he has no house and there is no point in asking a homeless person to go home, he told them to bring a large number of people and build his house if they are ready.",
        "After that, he told Ranil to come near the house and tell him to go home."
      ],
